Class TreeVisual

java.lang.Object
org.uclouvain.visualsearchtree.tree.TreeVisual
public class TreeVisual extends Object

TreeVisual: This Class instance return very basic profiling screen

This screen contain:

  • The Search Tree: [Tree]
  • The layout oft his screen is TreePane Object [TreePane]
